name: Viboyo Oweyo
description: '''Viboyo Oweyo''', real name '''Nsubuga Moses''', is a [[Uganda]]n musician and record producer. He is signed to [[Swangz Avenue]]. He's credited for his rap ups every year ( a compilation of events that happened throughout the year.) He has collaborated with music heavy weights like Radio and Weasel "Nyumbani", [[Cindy Sanyu]], "nyumirwa", [[Irene Ntale]], In "Banyilila", "St [[St. Nelly-Sade|Nelly Sade]] in rap up 2018", and [[GNL Zamba|Gnl Zamba]] vocals appeared on his rap up 2019.
